text: {'text': "I went there for my lunch and ordered the lunch special set for $15.50 ++, consisting of Chicken Katsu Curry, iced tea, soup of the day, and a scoop of Haagen Dazs ice cream. Large serving plate and one of the best tasting Japanese curries I've had. I chose the spiciest level but not really that spicy. Maybe I'm just used to eating spicy foods. Staff are attentive, and the place is cozy. Overall, it's a good dining experience, and I will definitely come back and try other dishes.", 'languageCode': 'en'}
